nudge_prompt:
Continue `{agent_name}` in `{worktree}`. Before you stop, run at least one new experiment family and update `{status_file}`. Do not merely restate existing conclusions. If your scope is truly complete, then and only then reply with `{done_marker} ...`.

Last message excerpt:
{last_message}

recovery_prompt:
The previous run for `{agent_name}` ended unexpectedly. Resume from the latest stable point in `{worktree}` without repeating settled work. Re-check status.json, identify the highest-value missing evidence, and execute it now. Reply with `{done_marker} ...` only if the scope is fully complete.

Last message excerpt:
{last_message}

stall_prompt:
The previous run for `{agent_name}` made no meaningful progress or appears stalled. Re-orient immediately: inspect status.json, identify the next missing evidence item, run the smallest experiment that resolves it, and record the result. Do not reply DONE unless every completion criterion is met.

Last message excerpt:
{last_message}
